<p><strong>SCP-2260：</strong>旅行日记<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shootdawhoop99" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2013215); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2013215&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600571120" alt="shootdawhoop99" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2013215)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shootdawhoop99" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2013215); return false;">shootdawhoop99</a></span><br />
